original_title: BREAKING – HUGE TRUMP VICTORY: The 9th Circuit Court of Appeals has just given President Trump the GREEN LIGHT to revoke legal status for 60,000 “migrants” from Honduras, Nicaragua, and Nepal. Fire up the deportation planes!  — The Donald
article_summary: The 9th Circuit Court of Appeals has granted President Trump authorization to revoke the legal status of 60,000 migrants from Honduras, Nicaragua, and Nepal, potentially leading to their deportation.</s>
